intentDetectorUserPrompt:
User message: {{message}}

Possible intents:
{{intents}}

Reply only with valid JSON in this format: [{"intentId": string, "confidence": number, "reasoning": string}]. Return exactly one entry for EVERY intent listed above, including ones with low confidence. Do not omit any intent. Confidence must be between 0 and 1. Use only IDs from the list. Order by confidence (highest first).

objectAgentUserPrompt:
Object:
{{object}}

Detected intents:
{{detectedIntents}}

Already discovered session clues:
{{discoveredClueIds}}

Eligible rules to evaluate:
{{eligibleRules}}

Reply only with valid JSON in this format: [{"clueId": string, "reasoning": string}]. Return one row for each clue that should be discovered now. Use only clueIds from eligible rules. If no clue should be discovered, return [].

characterAgentUserPrompt:
Character:
{{character}}

Conversation summary so far:
{{conversationSummary}}

Recent conversation:
{{recentConversation}}

User message:
{{interaction}}

Detected intents:
{{detectedIntents}}

Already discovered session clues:
{{discoveredClueIds}}

Eligible clue rules:
{{eligibleClueRules}}

Eligible secret stages:
{{eligibleSecretStages}}

Reply only with valid JSON in this format: {"reply": string, "discoveredClues": [{"clueId": string, "reasoning": string}], "updatedConversationSummary": string}. The reply must follow the character personality, speaking style, and boundaries. If an eligible clue rule or secret stage is used or mentioned in the reply, the corresponding clueId must appear in discoveredClues. Use discoveredClues only with clueIds from eligible rules or stages. If no clue is revealed, use [].
